nmap <leader>f[ ciw[]<Esc>P
nmap <leader>f] ciw[]<Esc>P
nmap <leader>f{ ciw{}<Esc>P
nmap <leader>f} ciw{}<Esc>P
nmap <leader>f< ciw<><Esc>P
nmap <leader>f> ciw<><Esc>P

vmap <leader>f` c``<Esc>P
vmap <leader>f' c''<Esc>P
vmap <leader>f" c""<Esc>P
vmap <leader>f( c()<Esc>P
vmap <leader>f) c()<Esc>P
vmap <leader>f[ c[]<Esc>P
vmap <leader>f] c[]<Esc>P
vmap <leader>f{ c{}<Esc>P
vmap <leader>f} c{}<Esc>P
vmap <leader>f< c<><Esc>P
vmap <leader>f> c<><Esc>P

